<br>
Keep in mind, there are always going to be disagreements about this camp. Even with the best of intentions there are going to be flared tempers etc. We can only hope that it is kept to a minimum.<br>
<br>
Stay safe out there.<br>
<br>
-Magada Caduceus<br>
